1. Skoro* se završila skola. (The school almost finished.)

2. Skoro* smo stigli u Srbiju. (We almost arrived in Serbia.)

3. Skoro* je bio kraj. (It was almost the end.)

4. Skoro* smo je videli. (We almost saw her.)

5. Skoro* je išla tamo. (She was almost going there.)

6. Skoro* smo završili. (We almost finished.)

7. Skoro* sam ga sreo. (I almost met him.)

8. Skoro* je bilo gotovo. (It was almost done.)